{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/ESLint-Prettier","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"73859ebb-31d9-5644-bc2c-ef274f543c60","html":"<h2 id=\"1-eslint개념-및-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-eslint%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"1 eslint개념 및 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. ESLint개념 및 설치</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 702px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1d19d74c0d89a5753c686b94bac18da0/eafa3/eslint.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/1d19d74c0d89a5753c686b94bac18da0/8ac56/eslint.webp 240w,\n/static/1d19d74c0d89a5753c686b94bac18da0/d3be9/eslint.webp 480w,\n/static/1d19d74c0d89a5753c686b94bac18da0/de2ca/eslint.webp 702w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/1d19d74c0d89a5753c686b94bac18da0/09b79/eslint.jpg 240w,\n/static/1d19d74c0d89a5753c686b94bac18da0/7cc5e/eslint.jpg 480w,\n/static/1d19d74c0d89a5753c686b94bac18da0/eafa3/eslint.jpg 702w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/1d19d74c0d89a5753c686b94bac18da0/eafa3/eslint.jpg\"\n            alt=\"ESLint\"\n            title=\"ESLint\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"--eslint란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#--eslint%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"  eslint란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✔  ESLint란?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>ESLint는   <strong>ES + Lint</strong> 의 합성어로 <strong>코드의 포맷팅과 품질관리</strong> 도구이다.   </li>\n<li>\n<p>ES는 EcmaScript(표준화된 스크립트 프로그래밍 언어)를 의미하고, Lint는 보푸라기라는 뜻으로 프로그래밍에서 에러가 있는 코드에 표시를 달아놓는것을 의미한다.  </p>\n<p>ESLint는 JS의 스타일 가이드를 따르지 않거나 문제가 있는 안티패턴들을 찾아주고, 일관된 코드스타일을 가질 수 있도록 도와주는 역할을 한다.  </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"--eslint-설치-및-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#--eslint-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"  eslint 설치 및 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✔  ESLint 설치 및 설정</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>vscode와 node.js를 다운받아 설치한다.</li>\n<li>terminal에서 <code class=\"language-text\">npm init</code>과 <code class=\"language-text\">npm install</code>을 실행하여 설치한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">yarn global add eslint</code> 혹은 <code class=\"language-text\">npm install -g eslint</code> 명령어를 사용하여 설치한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">eslint --init</code> 명령어로 초기화 해준 다음 다양한 설정값을 필요한 환경에 맞게 선택해준다.\nex)<br>\n<em>- ? How would you like to use ESLint?\n❯ To check syntax and find problems<br>\n? What type of modules does your project use?<br>\n❯ None of these<br>\n? Which framework does your project use?<br>\n❯ None of these<br>\n? Does your project use TypeScript?\n❯ No<br>\n? Where does your code run?<br>\n❯ browser<br>\n? What format do you want your config file to be in?<br>\n❯ JavaScript</em>  </li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-prettier개념-및-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-prettier%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"2 prettier개념 및 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Prettier개념 및 설치</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 874px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/443f03a6c41c9a1a464061397a6730bf/ea717/prettier.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42.91666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/443f03a6c41c9a1a464061397a6730bf/8ac56/prettier.webp 240w,\n/static/443f03a6c41c9a1a464061397a6730bf/d3be9/prettier.webp 480w,\n/static/443f03a6c41c9a1a464061397a6730bf/02c22/prettier.webp 874w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 874px) 100vw, 874px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/443f03a6c41c9a1a464061397a6730bf/09b79/prettier.jpg 240w,\n/static/443f03a6c41c9a1a464061397a6730bf/7cc5e/prettier.jpg 480w,\n/static/443f03a6c41c9a1a464061397a6730bf/ea717/prettier.jpg 874w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 874px) 100vw, 874px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/443f03a6c41c9a1a464061397a6730bf/ea717/prettier.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Prettier\"\n            title=\"Prettier\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"--prettier란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#--prettier%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"  prettier란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✔  Prettier란?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Prettier는 코드에 적용되어있던 스타일을 무시하고, 설정되어있는 정해진 규칙에 따라 <strong>자동으로 코드 스타일을 정리해 주는 코드 포멧터</strong>이다.</li>\n<li><strong>코드 포멧터</strong> ⇒ 개발자가 작성한 코드를 정해진 코딩 스타일을 따르도록 변환해주는 도구   </li>\n<li>코드의 한줄 최대 길이나, 탭의 길이, 따옴표 종류 등 <strong><u>코딩 스타일을 일괄적으로 통일</u></strong>해준다는 점에서, 특정 문법 요소를 사용하도록 해서 코드 퀄리티를 높여주는 ESLint와 차이점을 가지고 있다.  </li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"--prettier-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#--prettier-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"  prettier 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✔  Prettier 설치</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">npm i prettier -D -E</code> 명령어를 사용하여 Prettier를 설치한다.<br>\n( -E는 —save-exac의 축약형이다.)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">npx prettier test.js</code> 명령어로 Prettier를 실행한다. </li>\n<li>위 명령을 수행할 때 코드 자체를 수정하고 싶다면 —write옵션을 추가하여 <code class=\"language-text\">npx prettier --write test.js</code>와 같이 명령어를 사용해 준다.  </li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-리엑트에-eslint와-prettier-적용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EB%A6%AC%EC%97%91%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90-eslint%EC%99%80-prettier-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"3 리엑트에 eslint와 prettier 적용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 리엑트에 ESLint와 Prettier 적용하기</h2>\n<br/>\n<h3 id=\"-리엑트-프로젝트-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EB%A6%AC%EC%97%91%ED%8A%B8-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\" 리엑트 프로젝트 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✔ 리엑트 프로젝트 생성</h3>\n<p> 터미널에서 아래 명령어를 수행하여 리엑트 프로젝트를 생성해 준다.<br>\n명령어 : <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app 프로젝트이름 --use-npm</code><br>\n<br/></p>\n<h3 id=\"-prettier와-eslint를-같이-사용하려면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-prettier%EC%99%80-eslint%EB%A5%BC-%EA%B0%99%EC%9D%B4-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%A0%A4%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\" prettier와 eslint를 같이 사용하려면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✔ Prettier와 ESLint를 같이 사용하려면?</h3>\n<p> <strong>eslint-config-prettier</strong> 와 <strong>eslint-plugin-prettier</strong> 모듈을 추가해줘야 한다.<br>\n명령어 : <code class=\"language-text\">npm i eslint-plugin-prettier eslint-config-prettier -D</code>  </p>\n<p> 그 다음 <strong>VSCode의 Extensions: Marketplace</strong>로 들어가서 ESLint와 Prettier를 검색하여 설치한다.<br>\n<br/></p>\n<h3 id=\"-설정파일-수정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\" 설정파일 수정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✔ 설정파일 수정</h3>\n<p>  ♧  settings.json 파일을 열어 아래처럼 VSCode설정을 해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n// Set the default  \n\"editor.formatOnSave\": false,  \n// Enable per-language  \n\"[javascript]\": {  \n \"editor.formatOnSave\": true  \n},  \n\"editor.codeActionsOnSave\": {  \n // For ESLint  \n \"source.fixAll.eslint\": true  \n}  \n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>♧  터미널에서 아래 명령어를 수행하여 Airbnb Style Guide를 적용해준다.<br>\n명령어 : <code class=\"language-text\">npm i -D eslint-config-airbnb</code> </p>\n<p>♧  그 다음 <strong>.eslintrc.json</strong> 파일의 “extends”속성에 “airbnb”를 추가 해준다.  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n\"plugins\": [\"prettier\"],\n\"extends\": [\"eslint:recommended\", \"plugin:prettier/recommended\",\"airbnb\"],\n\"rules\": {\n\"prettier/prettier\": \"error\"\n}\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>♧  Prettier또한 ESLint와 마찬가지로 루트 경로에 <strong>.prettierrc.json</strong> 파일을 만들어 주고, 필요한 옵션을 골라 설정해 준다.  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">ex)\n{\n \"trailingComma\": \"es5\",\n \"tabWidth\": 2,\n \"semi\": true,\n \"singleQuote\": true\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"추가-참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"추가 참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>추가 참고</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://sunmon.github.io/vscode-eslint-prettier-setting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://sunmon.github.io/vscode-eslint-prettier-setting/</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://velog.io/@recordboy/ESLint-Prettier-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://velog.io/@recordboy/ESLint-Prettier-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://m.blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?isHttpsRedirect=true&#x26;blogId=dilrong&#x26;logNo=221413095305\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://m.blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?isHttpsRedirect=true&#x26;blogId=dilrong&#x26;logNo=221413095305</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/ESLint-Prettier","tagSlugs":["/tag/react/","/tag/eslint/","/tag/prettier/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-07-15T22:35:32.169Z","description":"ESLint와 Prettier 두가지를 비교하면서 두개의 개념에 대해 알아볼 수 있습니다. 또한, 